/// <summary>
/// NoPaidDataShortWindowMultiSymbolResearchV2 configuration. All entry thresholds, split schemes,
/// activation grids, and success criteria are fixed up-front in this file and are never tuned
/// against validation/holdout results. The frozen V1 BNB incubation track is not referenced,
/// modified, or regenerated by anything in this branch.
/// </summary>
